polychromatic (0.6.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Controller: Drop GTK/WebKit. Now uses PyQt5.
  * Controller: New UI design.
  * Controller: New troubleshooter for OpenRazer.
  * Controller: New configuration GUI for OpenRazer.
  * Controller: New 'Apply to All' feature.
  * Controller: New Preferences GUI.
  * Controller: New 'Device Info' and 'Inspect Matrix'.
  * Controller: New saved colour picker.
  * Controller: New icon picker - add support for Steam games and custom icons.
  * Controller: Warn when using incompatible configuration.
  * Controller: Drop --print-device-info parameter (use 'Device Info' instead)
  * Tray Applet: Add support for GTK Status Icon.
  * Tray Applet: New menu design.
  * Tray Applet: New option to delay autostart (to fix race conditions)
  * Helper: Replaces the tray applet autostart desktop launcher.
  * CLI: New command line interface via 'polychromatic-cli'
  * OpenRazer is no longer a hard dependency.
  * OpenRazer: Add support for multizoned hardware.
  * OpenRazer: Add support for battery status.
  * Add XDG desktop actions to desktop launcher.
  * New translations: pt_BR, fr_FR, fi_FI, ru, zh_CN
  * Change shebang to '/usr/bin/python3'
  * Build: Changed to meson/ninja.
  * Build: New locale scripts. Source language is now en_GB.
  * Build: Switch from 'lessc' to 'sassc'

 -- Luke Horwell <code@horwell.me>  Sat, 19 Dec 2020 16:09:50 +0100

